1252
01:37:03,092 --> 01:37:05,193
Sergeant Carroll calls them in for an interview.

1253
01:37:06,194 --> 01:37:08,735
He does that in conjunction with Officer Brooks.

1254
01:37:09,635 --> 01:37:14,398
And those that pass the interview level, their names get sent back up to me.

1255
01:37:14,858 --> 01:37:23,262
And then I send a letter over to the mayor requesting that they be appointed as reserve part-time traffic supervisors to fill vacancies that occur.

1256
01:37:24,373 --> 01:37:27,736
on a day-to-day, monthly, or for the year basis.

1257
01:37:28,596 --> 01:37:42,407
