2061
02:36:46,343 --> 02:36:47,204
Do you know off the top of your head?

2062
02:36:47,744 --> 02:36:49,586
It's if there's a financial hardship.

2063
02:36:51,567 --> 02:36:52,247
That's the main one.

2064
02:36:56,167 --> 02:37:02,152
I just think we spent 45 minutes on an issue that Councillor Carviello is probably right.

2065
02:37:02,312 --> 02:37:03,574
I know he does his due diligence.

2066
02:37:03,594 --> 02:37:06,356
He drives around more than any councillors that sit here.

2067
02:37:07,137 --> 02:37:09,999
And he checks out all the properties that he brings up and stuff.

2068
02:37:10,499 --> 02:37:15,283
So as I said, I'd like to reserve my judgment on that particular matter.

2069
02:37:15,804 --> 02:37:22,770
