2070
02:37:24,008 --> 02:37:31,794
And then we can actually tell if there's a major problem in the community, and we should be putting in some sort of zoning ordinance or zoning law.

2071
02:37:32,695 --> 02:37:36,597
But knowing that board, I will be shocked, like I said, if it's more than a dozen.

2072
02:37:36,938 --> 02:37:40,380
