2074
02:37:48,586 --> 02:37:53,370
And I know Attorney Arena, he is so tight when it comes to ethical standards.

2075
02:37:55,362 --> 02:37:57,163
It's amazing, so.

2076
02:38:11,967 --> 02:38:13,087
By address, Madam President.

2077
02:38:13,628 --> 02:38:20,590
