2087
02:38:42,924 --> 02:38:44,665
And I understand exactly where he's coming from.

2088
02:38:44,685 --> 02:38:46,766
And I certainly have concerns for the fabric of the neighborhood, too.

2089
02:38:47,547 --> 02:38:49,369
I certainly have concerns for the fabric of the neighborhood.

2090
02:38:49,729 --> 02:38:52,031
But I think that there's a proper process that's in place.

2091
02:38:52,071 --> 02:38:53,692
And I don't want to run rush out over the process.

2092
02:38:54,153 --> 02:39:02,880
And I certainly don't want to make any steps that are going to put us in a position to be politicizing an issue that shouldn't be politicizing, or politicizing a process that shouldn't be politicized.

2093
02:39:03,321 --> 02:39:05,122
So that's where I'm coming from, Madam President.

2094
02:39:05,162 --> 02:39:06,884
Insofar as the Tufts University situation,

2095
02:39:07,147 --> 02:39:09,067
