2096
02:39:09,707 --> 02:39:12,848
We don't have any oversight control or dictation over their operations.

2097
02:39:13,048 --> 02:39:21,129
We can make recommendations and we can make suggestions, but the zoning board of appeals and the rules and regulations that they fall under and that they are there to enforce are created by us.

2098
02:39:21,730 --> 02:39:22,290
We make them up.

2099
02:39:22,870 --> 02:39:23,610
We're the ones that make them.

2100
02:39:23,870 --> 02:39:25,050
We make the zoning ordinances.

2101
02:39:25,510 --> 02:39:27,691
